post.summary: Search all price and availability for parts
post.description:
This endpoint is providing for the price and discounts plus the available stock quantity in the queried warehouse.

The price and discounts are depending on the ***context of the sales***, that has the following multi dimensions:
- The department via which the sale is concluded
- The client buying the good
- The warehouse out of which the parts will be picked
- The sales channel(client, internal, warranty claim, insurance)
  - For the warranty claims, the trouble codemay influence the price/discounts
  - For internal transfer this is the cession code that is taking precedence

The stock quantity is also given from alternate warehouses andremote warehouses (from other companies sharing data with us)
ebndpoint: `POST /dealerships/{dealershipId}/parts/search`

CodeTypeID.title: type of the standard code (it refers to a fixed enumeration of "official" types)
CodeTypeID.description:
type of the standard code (it refers to a fixed enumeration of "official" types)

Below is the list of possible values
Value
Description
ACT
Repair order activity. ex: Maintenance, Repair, Internal, Body workshop, etc.
CASH
list of cashdesks (the default cash register depends on the user, therfore def=constant=0)
CAT
Document category. for the same purpose as the ACTivity for repair orders
CES
internal transfer code (for accounting integration of internal transfer invoices)
CIE
list of companies (dealer's rooftop within the same fiscal company)
CIV
civility titles for coding clients (ex: Mr, Mrs, Doctor, etc.)
CLI
client families: a statistical and accounting classification of clients
CLITX
Labour rates descriptions (this is not the value of rates that depends on this code and the nature of the client)
COUNTRY
countries (ISO codes)
CUR
currencies (ISO codes)
DSCLBR
client's discount codes for labours. if special discounts must be granted to TAXI drivers then a labour-discount code having the description "TAXI" must be created first
DSCPACK
client's discount codes for packages. if special discounts must be granted to insurance companies then a labour-discount code having the description "Insurance" must be created first
DSCPART
client's discount codes for spare parts. if special discounts must be granted to the agents from the brand then a labour-discount code having the description "Agents" must be created first
FAM
spare parts families. statistical and accounting classification for instance to separate tyres from oils and from mechanical parts
LANG
Languages (for example NL FR)
MEC
Mechanics names. They are used for openning repair orders and setting a timeslot in the department planner
NCDEPT
new-car sales department (the default dept depends on the user, therfore def=constant=0)
PAY
list of payment modes (not to confuse with cash registers!)
PRTSUPL
Spare Parts suppliers used to codify the references in the pricelist
RCP
list of receptionists (the default ID depends on the user, therfore def=constant=0) they are used to create a repair order and for the appointments in the department planner
SDEPT
shop departments (over the counter sales) (the default dept depends on the user, therfore def=constant=0)
SEX
gender 1=male / 2=female
SMAN
Salesman (of vehicles)
STKTYPE
Types of stock (for vehicles)  a statistical and accounting classification of hold places of vehicles
TEAM
list of teams of mechanics
UCDEPT
used-car sales department (the default dept depends on the user, therfore def=constant=0)
USER
list of users / logins
VATA
list of VAT codes applicable to "articles" parts, labours, packages, vehicles, etc.
VATC
list of VAT codes applicable to clients
VATPCT
list of VAT percentages the ID is a triplet of codes separated by pipes, format is VATC | VATA | VAT-ID ==> vat percentage
VEHBRAND
vehicle brands
WDEPT
workshop department (the default dept depends on the user therfore def=constant=0)
WHPART
warehouse for spare parts (the default warehouse depends on the user therfore def=constant=0)
WHVEH
warehouse for vehicles in stocks (the default warehouse depends on the user therfore def=constant=0)
ZIP
list of zip codes
